{
  "stem": "19982.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I felt that I'm punished because I'm not good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So my parents are sending me away, that they don't want me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I-- I-- I felt so terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was crying and screaming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then my father would force [INAUDIBLE] me on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were going with horses-- a wagon and horses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There weren't-- we-- our town had only one car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There weren't any cars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was one car, which one person had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So everybody went with a wagon and horses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he put me on this wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the wagon went away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they-- like, I saw them [INAUDIBLE] was waving goodbye.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was crying without a stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "All the way, I-- besides-- and I was frightened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Even though I knew the people very well, I was so frightened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the most of it, I-- I felt that my parents don't love me anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They don't want me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They're sending me away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I mean, I really didn't know for many years-- I didn't know what the courage it took to send-- [SOBBING] to have only child [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and to send her away, not knowing what's going to be.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And of course, I remember my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He said, be good, be nice, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and remember who you are.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Remember that you are a daughter of Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I was screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We are going-- I was oblivious to everything what's going around me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I was just crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Everything what I wanted-- I didn't care about anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Everything what I wanted is to go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we were traveling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And the Germans were right behind us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "You know, like, we could hear the-- the-- the fighting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We could hear everything right-- we could sometimes could hear the-- could see the fire.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
